file.name: one-of-all-of.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: oneOf allOf
  version: '1.0'
paths: {}
components:
  schemas:
    PropertyInfo:
      oneOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/IntegerProperty'
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/StringProperty'
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/ObjectProperty'
      discriminator:
        propertyName: type
        mapping:
          int: '#/components/schemas/IntegerProperty'
          string: '#/components/schemas/StringProperty'
    AbstractProperty:
      type: object
      properties:
        type:
          type: string
    IntegerProperty:
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/AbstractProperty'
        - type: object
          properties:
            value:
              type: integer
    StringProperty:
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/AbstractProperty'
        - type: object
          properties:
            value:
              type: string
    ObjectProperty:
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/AbstractProperty'
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/ObjectValue'
    ObjectValue:
      type: object
      required:
        - id
      nullable: true
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
